  <Title>New Death Penalty Sytem</Title>
  <Type>1</Type>
  <Content>Upon death, characters will not drop items in their inventory. Items that break on death will still break. Gold and equipped items will still drop or break. So only items in your inventory, that would normally drop in a pile on death, will no longer drop. They will remain in your inventory. All items will still take a durability penalty.

Also, the following items have been made into non-break items, which means that they will not disappear upon death.

Black Pearl Ring
Mythril Boots 
Dark Belt
Light Belt 
Desert Dunes Necklaces
Black Stone Rings
Tristar Rings
Cathonic Shield
Andor salve earrings
